{"segment":2,"line_start":36,"line_end":72,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":null,"text":"\"我……我相信你。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"line_start":52,"line_end":52}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_cui_nong","updates":{"rag_refs":[40],"status":"为傅红雪挡下王大洪一剑而死","source_refs":[{"chapter":40,"line_start":16,"line_end":52,"text":"但翠浓却恰巧在这一瞬间张开眼，恰巧看见了墙上的影子。她连想都没有想，突然用尽全身力量，推开了傅红雪，用自己的身子，去挡这一剑。剑光一闪，已刺入了她的背脊。一阵无法形容的刺痛，使得她只觉得整个人都仿佛已被撕裂。可是她的眼睛，却还是在看着傅红雪"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_fu_hong_xue","type":"牺牲挚爱","intensity":100,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"临死前仍求傅红雪相信自己，证明情感真挚。"}]},{"id":"char_fu_hong_xue","updates":{"rag_refs":[40],"status":"目睹翠浓为自己牺牲，仇恨与悲痛骤然加深","source_refs":[{"chapter":40,"line_start":44,"line_end":74,"text":"傅红雪又倒在床上，看着她，看着她混合着痛苦和安慰的眼光，看着她凄凉而甜蜜的微笑。他的心已碎了。翠浓看着他，终于挣扎着说出了一句话。\"你要相信我，我真的不知道他是谁，也不知道他要害你。\"傅红雪道：\"我……我相信你。\"他用力咬着牙，但满眶热泪，"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_cui_nong","type":"痛失恋人","intensity":100,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"翠浓死亡成为他新的深仇。"}]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":74,"line_end":118,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"你一定想知道我究竟是什么人。\"","tone":"轻笑","chapter":40,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"我是来要你命的人！\"","tone":"激动","chapter":40,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_wang_da_hong","text":"\"你也是那天在梅花庵外行刺的凶手？\"","tone":"平静","chapter":40,"line_start":86,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"我不是，我要杀的只是你！\"","tone":"激动","chapter":40,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_wang_da_hong","text":"\"为什么？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":40,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"你能杀别人，别人为什么不能杀你？\"","tone":"冷笑","chapter":40,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_wang_da_hong","text":"\"我不认得你。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"你也不认得郭威，但你却杀了他，还杀了那可怜的孩子。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"line_start":96,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_wang_da_hong","text":"\"你是为他们来复仇的？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":40,"line_start":100,"line_end":100},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"不是。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_wang_da_hong","text":"\"你为的是什么？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":40,"line_start":104,"line_end":104},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"杀人的理由有很多，并不一定是为了仇恨。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"li