{"segment":5,"line_start":160,"line_end":196,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_wang_da_hong","text":"\"你已后悔？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":40,"line_start":174,"line_end":174},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"我只后悔没有听信一个人的话。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_wang_da_hong","text":"\"什么话？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":40,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"他本来要我先毁了你这柄刀的。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"line_start":180,"line_end":180},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_wang_da_hong","text":"\"先毁这柄刀？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":40,"line_start":182,"line_end":182},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"这柄刀虽然并不特别，但是对你来说，它的价值却很特别。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"line_start":184,"line_end":186},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_wang_da_hong","text":"\"哦？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":40,"line_start":188,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"因为这柄刀就像是你的拐杖一样，若没有这柄刀的话，你只不过是个可怜的跛子而已，你只有在手里握着这柄刀的时候，才能站得直。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"line_start":190,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_hong","speaker_name":"王大洪","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"\"这些话当然不是我说的，因为我以前根本就没见过你，根本就不了解你。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":40,"line_start":196,"line_end":198}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_cui_du_duan_jian","name":"淬毒短剑","type":"兵器","owner":"char_wang_da_hong","one_line":"王大洪用来暗算傅红雪的青蓝色淬毒短剑。","description":"剑光青蓝、出手迅捷，剑上淬有剧毒，只要划破皮肤便足以置人于死地，是幕后之人交给王大洪的暗杀兵器。","effects":["刺杀","剧毒"],"origin":"幕后主使交给王大洪用于暗算傅红雪","rarity":"稀有","related_characters":["char_wang_da_hong","char_f